---
title: Montreal-Spiced Chicken and Mango Salad with Candied Walnuts and Balsamic Dressing
description: A quick flash in a hot pan transforms walnuts and brown sugar into a deliciously sweet and crunchy salad topper – to finish off a salad with perfectly seared chicken and tropical, juicy mango. This satisfying salad is bound to become part of your weeknight repertoire.
